These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
There 2 different types of food: nectarine, pear
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, iced-tea
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is not the person eating pear##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | pear   | nectarine  |
| Sport   | hot-chocolate | iced-tea |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: photography, writing
2 different pets are kept: goat, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the owner of the goat is not the person who's hobby is writing##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | photography | writing      |
| Pet    | goat  | guinea-pig |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
