.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-4::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, montecristo
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, hamster
1. the montecristo-smoker is not the owner of the goldfish##6
2. the montecristo-smoker is somewhere to the right of the havana-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2      |
| Food   | havana  | montecristo |
| Pet    | goldfish | hamster    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-5::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, june
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, lacrosse
1. the person who's birthday is in june is not the person who's sport is lacrosse##6
2. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Movie-Genre   | july  | june |
| Sport         | lacrosse | golf      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-6::.
There 2 different types of food: raspberry, apricot
There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, polish
