.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-7::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, social-worker
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: water-polo, parkour
1. the accountant is in an odd position##4
2. the accountant is not the person who's sport is parkour##6

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1      |       2       |
| Job   | accountant | social-worker |
| Pet   | water-polo       | parkour       |

